e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事?<br />\n美容姐個個都岩做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170611/s00001/1497172693029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170611%2Fs00001%2F1497172693029&d=X%2BSTMYEMSAHrUNu%2FG3a63%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3abac5fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170611%2Fs00001%2F1497172693029&h=c45a9a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170611/s00001/1497172693029</a><br />\n<br />\n【短片】美容院施「美男計」強迫顧客買療程　民主黨接42個案涉款210萬元　女學生及專業人士亦中招 (17:55) <br />\n<br />\n美容院黑店騙財手法層出不窮。民主黨自去年12月起，收到42宗求助個案，女事主年齡介乎26歲至47歲，包括女學生及專業人士，事主於網上被陌生男子兜搭，投其所好展開話題。當事主應邀見面後，即被帶到美容院強迫購買美容療程，涉及總金額超過210萬元。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨美容事主投訴熱線接獲42宗個案，均與同一間美容院有關，民主黨消費者權益政策副發言人袁海文懷疑騙案由一條龍集團策劃。<br />\n<br />\n袁海文指出，該美容院於簽署合約時懷疑隱瞞細節及誇大療效等，涉嫌觸犯欺詐罪及商品說明條例，民主黨將成立聯盟，與事主集體報警及海關。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170611/s00001/1497172693029#sthash.C7XrxOVT.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170611%2Fs00001%2F1497172693029%23sthash.C7XrxOVT.dpuf&d=X%2BSTMYEMSAHrUNu%2FG3a63%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=50ac9392\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170611%2Fs00001%2F1497172693029%23sthash.C7XrxOVT.dpuf&h=248b6b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170611/s00001/1497172693029#sthash.C7XrxOVT.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"066c44c103945e215c8ba48850cc43faada619f4","tid":279554,"uid":31758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25bac256601b136d96c161ada2b10de36a0785f","tid":279554,"uid":16318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:19:28.000Z","msg":"中同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗做咩咁耐都唔捉佢，又出曬樣又有名，又有咁多受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然都係d 女太on 9..."},{"pid":"c51c4be0aba7e8fd31cd2aaa1d5d033939ec80a1","tid":279554,"uid":31758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}